By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 5
  Paragraph: 16
Title: The Sign Of Virtue Complete
---
In Lu there was a man named Shu-shan No-Toes who had had his foot cut
off. Stumping along, he went to see Confucius.
